flowchart TD
    LoadModel[<b>Load Whisper model</b><br/>from local snapshot or download if not present]
    LoadModel --> Subs[Create subscriptions:<br/><b>/audio_and_device_info</b><br/><b>/vad</b><br/><b>/speech_activity_detection</b>]

    Subs --> AudioMsg[Audio message received]
    AudioMsg --> PushBuffer[Append chunk to<br/>rolling audio buffer<br/>evict chunks older than 35s]
    PushBuffer --> AudioMsg

    Subs --> SpeakerMsg[Speaker ID message received]
    SpeakerMsg --> StoreSpeaker[Store current speaker ID]
    StoreSpeaker --> SpeakerMsg

    Subs --> VADMsg[VAD probability received]
    VADMsg --> ThreshCheck{Probability &gt;<br/>VAD threshold?}

    ThreshCheck -->|Yes| SpeechStart[Record speech start time<br/>cancel any pending<br/>silence timer]
    SpeechStart --> DurationCheck{Speech exceeds<br/>max chunk duration?}
    DurationCheck -->|Yes| ForceSplit[Find quietest point<br/>in middle of chunk<br/>and split there]
    ForceSplit --> Transcribe
    DurationCheck -->|No| VADMsg

    ThreshCheck -->|No| SilenceTimer[Start silence timer<br/>in background thread]
    SilenceTimer --> TimerWait{Silence 1s timer<br/>elapsed without<br/>new speech?}
    TimerWait -->|Cancelled - speech resumed| VADMsg
    TimerWait -->|Elapsed| Transcribe[Extract audio from buffer<br/>speech start to silence end<br/>with pre-buffer prefix]

    Transcribe --> LangResolve{Language<br/>configured?}
    LangResolve -->|Fixed language| RunWhisper
    LangResolve -->|Auto-detect| DetectLang[Run language detection<br/>pick best from allowed list]
    DetectLang --> RunWhisper[Run Whisper model<br/>batched or standard inference<br/>with VAD filter]

    RunWhisper --> HasText{Transcript<br/>non-empty?}
    HasText -->|No| ResetTiming[Reset speech timing]
    HasText -->|Yes| PublishResult[Publish <b>/speech_result</b><br/>SpeechResult:<br/>transcript, speaker ID, language]
    PublishResult --> ROS4HRI{ROS4HRI<br/>enabled?}
    ROS4HRI -->|Yes| PublishVoice[Publish to<br/><b>/humans/voices/&lt;speaker_id&gt;/speech</b>]
    PublishVoice --> ResetTiming
    ROS4HRI -->|No| ResetTiming
    ResetTiming --> VADMsg

